bor/2khdyHiysXFCvt1JfQN-z5B3IfA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /70781237/acastro_220321_5154_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Apple Watch Series 9、Ultra 2 和第二代 SE 之间，有比以往更多的选择。我们将帮助您对它们进行分类。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se -best-smartwatch-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-13T13:36:39-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-13T13:36:39-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊最新 Fire TV Stick 4K Max 降价促销</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;亚马逊 Fire TV Stick 4K Max 流媒体棒，其遥控器位于电视机前的一碗爆米花旁边。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/c2w5AOwTK1HuYc10ScUaxIDnosc=/0x29:1210x836/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72861181/Fire_TV_Stick_4K_Max_Image_1.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新款 Fire TV Stick 4K Max 看起来就像亚马逊的任何旧流媒体棒一样，但其升级最突出的是内部。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：亚马逊&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;bQkCDb&quot;>;随着黑色星期五促销活动在早些时候持续不断，更多最新设备将首次发售或创下新低。一个例子是&lt;strong>;亚马逊的新款 Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/strong>;，它在几个月前刚刚推出，现在在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/news/FireTV-Stick/Fire-TV-Stick-20&quot; 上以 39.99 美元（折扣 20 美元）的价格出售。 amazon.com/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckZO8Hjol79&quot;>;最佳购买&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7RlfBC&quot;>;亚马逊的新款旗舰 4K 流媒体棒很像 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22715206/amazon- fire-tv-stick-4k-max-review&quot;>;上一代型号&lt;/a>;，